    {
      "id": "69f9ec6ce2671dd01d3cb18a",
      "text": "大腿骨骨幹部骨折",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777986721,
      "updated": 1777986721
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9eca100000000000f7e33",
      "text": "[大腿骨]（太ももの骨）の真ん中（[骨幹部]）の骨折",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777986721,
      "updated": 1778023603
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ecc100000000000f7e35",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777986754,
      "updated": 1777986754
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ecab00000000000f7e34",
      "text": "> [https://scrapbox.io/files/69f9ecf42dc79442f0d5f0db.webp]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777986732,
      "updated": 1777986806
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9ece900000000000f7e3b",
      "text": "> [https://www.jikosoudan.net/article/13479757.html 大腿骨骨幹部骨折の基礎知識 | 八文字社会保険労務士行政書士事務所]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777986794,
      "updated": 1777986794
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9eea300000000000f7e3d",
      "text": "\t4週間で松葉杖歩行が可能になり、6週間で体重負荷による歩行が可能になり、骨癒合には10～12週間かかると言われている、と書かれている。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777987236,
      "updated": 1777987542
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9efdb00000000000f7e40",
      "text": " \tかなりの長期戦……。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1777987548,
      "updated": 1777987642
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa012500000000002812d5",
      "text": " ここが折れるとしばしばめっちゃ血が出るので命が危ないイメージ",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777991973,
      "updated": 1777992063
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9eea300000000000f7e3e",
      "text": "  皮膚の色は変化なかったが、だいぶ太もも膨らんでた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777987236,
      "updated": 1777992056
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa03950000000000bd9f6a",
      "text": "  大変だ[imo.icon]",
      "userId": "5ad57975d54cd50014068484",
      "created": 1777992598,
      "updated": 1777992625
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa812000000000006a6a26",
      "text": "  複雑骨折ではなかったのが不幸中の幸い[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778024737,
      "updated": 1778024753
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa01360000000000af1b30",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777991990,
      "updated": 1777991993
    },
    {
      "id": "69f9eee600000000000f7e3f",
      "text": "現代の病院でよくやる治療法は、、",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777987302,
      "updated": 1777991947
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa00f200000000002812d1",
      "text": " https://www.jsfr.jp/ippan/condition/ip33.html",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777991923,
      "updated": 1777992003
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa013e00000000002812d6",
      "text": " スタンダードは[髄内釘治療]という手術らしい。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777992003,
      "updated": 1777992043
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa018800000000002812d8",
      "text": "  この釘にあたるものが[takker.icon]さんのいってたチタン合金か。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777992073,
      "updated": 1777992103
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa016800000000002812d7",
      "text": "  ずいないてい入れた[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1777992043,
      "updated": 1777992185
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa01c100000000002812d9",
      "text": " 小児では手術しなくても治りやすいので[保存的治療]をすることもある。",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777992129,
      "updated": 1777992156
    },
    {
      "id": "69fa023600000000002812dc",
      "text": "  ギプス固定など",
      "userId": "60c9f2f6c225a50020b8bbfc",
      "created": 1777992247,
      "updated": 1777992249
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabb26000000000044f77c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778039589,
      "updated": 1778039589
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabb28000000000044f77d",
      "text": "石膏でガッチリ固定状態からのスタートなんだろか。[taktamur.icon]",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778039592,
      "updated": 1778039634
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabb53000000000044f77f",
      "text": " 友人知人が落書きするあれ",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778039635,
      "updated": 1778039654
    },
    {
      "id": "69fbc44d0000000000601c17",
      "text": " 石膏使いませんでした[takker.icon]",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1778107470,
      "updated": 1778107479
    },
    {
      "id": "69fbc4570000000000601c18",
      "text": "  腰に小さな穴をあけて、そこから大腿骨に[髄内釘]をいれたみたい",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1778107479,
      "updated": 1778107531
    },
    {
      "id": "69fabb3a000000000044f77e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "58a90dd3ee5de7001150db17",
      "created": 1778039610,
      "updated": 1778039610
    }
  ]
}